   California Technology, Trade & Commerce Agency Welcome to the new Web
   site of the California Technology, Trade and Commerce Agency. It's a
   dynamic and interactive portal into the world's 5th largest economy.
   Here, you'll find the tools you need for business success.

    FEATURED INFORMATION
   [spacer.gif]
   We can help your business grow
   If you want to expand your business, we can help you find the right
   place to locate in California.
   More...
   [spacer.gif]
   The California Infrastructure and Economic Development Bank
   We can provide low-cost infrastructure loans to public agencies, and
   issue conduit revenue bonds for private companies and nonprofits.
   More...
   [spacer.gif]
   We'll help your company go global
   We can help you develop and sell your product to our foreign trade
   partners.
   More...
   [spacer.gif]
   Technology and Innovation Grants
   Need help getting your innovative or high-tech product off the ground?
   More...
   [spacer.gif]
   How you can save money on energy costs
   Find out how other businesses saved big bucks with their innovative
   energy-saving ideas.
   More...
   [spacer.gif]
   Incentives for Filming in California
   Filming in California has never been so financially rewarding!
   More...
